],"information":{"description":[null,"When you play the Lunar New Year Step Up Gacha, you will receive set rewards at each Step.\nThis gacha has 5 Steps. Each play moves you up one Step.\nDuring the gacha period, the first Step can be played for 2500 Stars. The Stars required for each Step will decrease as you play.\n\nThe rewards for each Step are as follows.\nStep 1: 10,000 Coins + 2 Studio Tickets (Premium) + Moca Stamp\nStep 2: 10,000 Coins + 2 Boost Drinks + Hina Stamp\nStep 3: 10,000 Coins + 2 Skill Tickets (Triple) + Sayo Stamp\nStep 4: 10,000 Coins + 1 ★3+ Gacha Ticket + Kaoru Stamp\nStep 5: 10,000 Coins + 1 Skill Ticket (Premium) + Tae Stamp\n\nFeaturing ★★ and higher members! \nOne ★★★ member guaranteed!\nNew ★★★ and higher members come with a new costume!",null,null,null],"term":[null,"2019/02/05 08:00 ～ 2019/02/10 07:59 UTC",null,null,null],"newMemberInfo":[null,null,null,null,null],"notice":[null,"・All members drop with their pre-Training images.\n・Duplicate members may drop when playing the gacha.\n・Duplicate members will automatically be sent to the Waiting Room.\n・Each individual drop is performed according to the gacha drop rates. Example: 100 plays will not necessarily result in 1 drop of a member that has a 1% drop rate.\n・Members from the Sunset Smile Star Gacha will be featured in this gacha as well. However, drop rates will vary.\n・For more on featured members and drop rates, check Gacha Details.\n・Even in the event that the Gacha Results screen did not display because the app was forced to close or connection was interrupted, members will be obtained. Please check the Member List or the Waiting Room.\n・Campaign schedule may be subject to change without prior notice. ",null,null,null]}}